Title: Finding Dory Official Trailer #2 (2016) - Ellen DeGeneres, Albert Brooks Movie HD
Comment: Finding Dory is one of those rare sequels that manages to surpass it's predecessor. Writers Andrew Stanton and Victoria Strouse have written a delightful sequel with a beautiful new storyline where the surrounding events and conflicts are different from the last movie and new wonderful characters are introduced while keeping some of the things that made Finding Nemo, one of my favorite animated movies. The voice cast led by Ellen DeGeneres, Albert Brooks, Hayden Rolence, Ed O...'Neill, Kaitlin Olson, Ty Burrell, Diane Keaton and Eugene Levy all give lovely performances. Andrew Stanton does a great job directing this movie, the animation by Pixar Animation Studios is cheerful as always and I really liked the movie's jolly message about Dory learning that her defect doesn't define who she is and the way she accomplishes tasks is unique. 5/5 stars.
